quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  53,33,Afara'ayta Al-Ladhī Tawallá
  53,34,Wa 'A`ţá Qalīlāan Wa 'Akdá
  53,35,A`indahu `Ilmu Al-Ghaybi Fahuwa Yará
  53,36,Am Lam Yunabba' Bimā Fī Şuĥufi Mūsá
  53,37,Wa 'Ibrāhīma Al-Ladhī Wa Ffá
  53,38,Allā Taziru Wāziratun Wizra 'Ukhrá
  53,39,Wa 'An Laysa Lil'insāni 'Illā Mā Sa`á
  53,40,Wa 'Anna Sa`yahu Sawfa Yurá
  53,41,Thumma Yujzāhu Al-Jazā'a Al-'Awfá
  53,42,Wa 'Anna 'Ilá Rabbika Al-Muntahá
  53,43,Wa 'Annahu Huwa 'Ađĥaka Wa 'Abká
  53,44,Wa 'Annahu Huwa 'Amāta Wa 'Aĥyā
  53,45,Wa 'Annahu Khalaqa Az-Zawjayni Adh-Dhakara Wa Al-'Unthá
  53,46,Min Nuţfatin 'Idhā Tumná
  53,47,Wa 'Anna `Alayhi An-Nash'ata Al-'Ukhrá
  53,48,Wa 'Annahu Huwa 'Aghná Wa 'Aqná
  53,49,Wa 'Annahu Huwa Rabbu Ash-Shi`rá
  53,50,Wa 'Annahu 'Ahlaka `Ādāan Al-'Ūlá
  53,51,Wa Thamūda Famā 'Abqá
  53,52,Wa Qawma Nūĥin Min Qablu 'Innahum Kānū Hum 'Ažlama Wa 'Aţghá
  53,53,Wa Al-Mu'utafikata 'Ahwá
  53,54,Faghashāhā Mā Ghashá
  53,55,Fabi'ayyi 'Ālā'i Rabbika Tatamārá
  53,56,Hādhā Nadhīrun Mina An-Nudhuri Al-'Ūlá
  53,57,Azifati Al-'Āzifahu
  53,58,Laysa Lahā Min Dūni Allāhi Kāshifahun
  53,59,Afamin Hādhā Al-Ĥadīthi Ta`jabūna
  53,60,Wa Tađĥakūna Wa Lā Tabkūna
  53,61,Wa 'Antum Sāmidūna
  53,62,Fāsjudū Lillāhi Wa A`budū